{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "mtpx-minimal-app-collection",
    "name": "mtpx minimal service api",
    "description": "Collection para testar o exemplo minimal-app do Multpex Framework.\n\n## Auth\n\nExecute **Auth > Set Dev Token** primeiro para configurar o `accessToken` no environment.\nIsso habilita os endpoints protegidos (DELETE, Admin).\n\n## Endpoints\n\n- **GET /minimal-app/items** - Listar items\n- **GET /minimal-app/items/:id** - Buscar item por ID\n- **POST /minimal-app/items** - Criar item (com validação Zod)\n- **DELETE /minimal-app/items/:id** - Deletar item (requer auth + role admin)\n\n## Admin\n\n- **GET /minimal-app/admin/stats** - Estatísticas (requer role admin)\n\n## Health\n\n- **GET /minimal-app/health** - Health check\n- **GET /minimal-app/ready** - Readiness check\n- **GET /minimal-app/live** - Liveness check",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{accessToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Configuração de autenticação para endpoints protegidos.\n\nO token de dev está no `.env` da infra (`DEV_TOKEN`).\nEste request seta a variável `accessToken` no environment para uso automático nos demais requests.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Set Dev Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// DEV_TOKEN pré-gerado (admin role, 10-year expiry, signed with dev-secret)",
                  "// Regenere com: cd mtpx-framework-dev-infra && bun run gen-dev-token.ts",
                  "const devToken = 'eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJkZXYtdXNlciIsInRlbmFudF9pZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJyb2xlcyI6WyJhZG1pbiIsInVzZXIiXSwicGVybWlzc2lvbnMiOlsicmVhZCIsIndyaXRlIl0sImlhdCI6MTc3MTg5MDI0OCwiZXhwIjoyMDg3MjUwMjQ4fQ.Ub_eCs6TPm-Hcj283y7s2_E6iSf9kA9Kc_LkfQcYOYs';",
                  "",
                  "pm.environment.set('accessToken', devToken);",
                  "console.log('accessToken configurado com DEV_TOKEN (admin role)');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Health returns 200 (token validation)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('accessToken is set', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.environment.get('accessToken')).to.not.be.empty;",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Faz um health check e configura o accessToken no environment.\n\nExecute este request primeiro para autenticar os endpoints protegidos (DELETE items, Admin Stats)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Health check returns 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status is healthy', function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.equal('healthy');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "health"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Readiness Check",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Readiness returns 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/ready",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "ready"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Liveness Check",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Liveness returns 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/live",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "live"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Items",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Items",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('List returns 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has items array', function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.items).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has instanceId', function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.instanceId).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/items",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "items"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Items (Filter by Name)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/items?name=widget",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "items"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "name", "value": "widget" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Item by ID",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Get item returns 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has item data', function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.id).to.equal('1');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.name).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/items/1",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "items", "1"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Item Not Found",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Returns 404 or error', function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.error).to.equal('Not found');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/items/nonexistent",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "items", "nonexistent"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Item",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Create returns 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has new item', function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.id).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.name).to.equal('New Product');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.price).to.equal(49.99);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "// Save item ID for later tests",
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.id) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('itemId', jsonData.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"New Product\",\n  \"price\": 49.99,\n  \"tags\": [\"new\", \"featured\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/items",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "items"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Item (Validation Error)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Validation fails', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(400);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"\",\n  \"price\": -10\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/items",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "items"]
            },
            "description": "Testa validação Zod: name vazio e price negativo devem falhar"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Item (No Auth)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Returns 401 unauthorized', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(401);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/items/1",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "items", "1"]
            },
            "description": "Deve falhar sem autenticação"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Item (With Auth)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Delete successful or not found', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 404]);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/items/{{itemId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "items", "{{itemId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Requer auth com role admin. Usa itemId salvo do teste Create."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Stats (No Auth)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Returns 401 unauthorized', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(401);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/admin/stats",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "admin", "stats"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Stats (With Auth)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Returns stats', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.totalItems).to.be.a('number');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.totalValue).to.be.a('number');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/minimal-app/admin/stats",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["minimal-app", "admin", "stats"]
            },
            "description": "Requer auth com role admin"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
